OL,3,CVehicles and electronic devices seized
OL,4,Cin probe into Dunmurry blast
OL,6,FTwo vehicles and electronic devices
OL,7,Fhave been seized by detectives probing
OL,8,Fa car bomb attack on a police station
OL,9,Fin Co Antrim earlier this year.
OL,11,FA delivery driver was hijacked and a
OL,12,Fdevice placed in his car before he was
OL,13,Fordered to drive to Dunmurry police
OL,14,Fstation on Saturday April 25.
OL,16,FThe car exploded outside the station
OL,17,Fas people were being evacuated.
OL,19,FNobody was injured in the incident
OL,20,Fwhich sparked widespread condemnation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
