OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781723470
OL,3,CVehicles and electronic devices seized
OL,4,Cin probe into Dunmurry blast
OL,6,FIn a statement on Tuesday, a police
OL,7,Fspokesperson said detectives from the
OL,8,FPSNI's Terrorism Investigation Unit,
OL,9,Fassisted by local policing and
OL,10,Foperational support officers,
OL,11,Fconducted searches in west Belfast as
OL,12,Fpart of the investigation into the
OL,13,Fattack.
OL,15,F"Two vehicles and a number of items,
OL,16,Fincluding electronic devices, were
OL,17,Fseized," they said.
